Another monthly contest come to the end. Thank you all for participation.

I wanted problems to be very interesting. In some cases I think I failed, but there was a couple of worthwile tasks (at least for me :P ) My favourite four: P15, P18, P19, P20

Which subject do you want to raise this time?
